780
01:02:16,100 --> 01:02:18,600
...and we never had this conversation?
- Why?

781
01:02:18,700 --> 01:02:20,700
If we open the door
and go down that road...

782
01:02:21,200 --> 01:02:26,700
...any chance that we had of having
something normal will just be gone.

783
01:02:27,500 --> 01:02:28,700
It just will.

784
01:02:28,800 --> 01:02:32,600
Believe me. I have enough
experience of that now.

785
01:02:34,100 --> 01:02:36,800
I mean, sometimes, I mean...

786
01:02:37,000 --> 01:02:40,600
You know, knowing everything
about someone, it's...

787
01:02:40,800 --> 01:02:43,600
You know, it seems nice, but, really...

788
01:02:43,700 --> 01:02:47,200
...maybe it's actually better
to hold stuff back.

789
01:02:47,400 --> 01:02:49,300
I hear you.

790
01:02:49,500 --> 01:02:53,800
But you can understand. I'm curious.

791
01:02:53,900 --> 01:02:57,400
No, of course. I mean, yeah. Yeah.

792
01:02:58,500 --> 01:03:00,300
Please?

