01:10:32,600 --> 01:10:34,200
Two secs, Marcus.

878
01:10:35,500 --> 01:10:37,300
DENNIS [WHISPERS]:
We're gonna need another bed.

879
01:10:37,900 --> 01:10:40,200
Upstairs? Should I take yours?

880
01:10:49,900 --> 01:10:51,600
DENNIS: You all right?
