01:12:22,500 --> 01:12:24,000
CLARE:
Let's get it sorted as soon as possible.

895
01:12:24,200 --> 01:12:25,200
Thanks.

896
01:12:25,400 --> 01:12:27,500
CLARE:
All right, Marcus? See you soon, mate.

