about the vision I had.

925
01:16:23,600 --> 01:16:24,900
- Sure, go ahead.
- Yeah.

926
01:16:25,000 --> 01:16:28,700
It was a very peaceful sensation.

927
01:16:29,200 --> 01:16:33,700
Everything was quiet.
Darkness everywhere.

928
01:16:33,900 --> 01:16:37,000
And a light was catching my eyes.

929
01:16:37,200 --> 01:16:39,700
And I was hearing the sound
of a gentle wind.

930
01:16:39,900 --> 01:16:40,900
ROUSSEAU:
Mm-hm.

931
01:16:41,600 --> 01:16:44,200
A feeling of weightlessness?

932
01:16:44,300 --> 01:16:45,700
Yes.

933
01:16:45,900 --> 01:16:48,400
A 360 perspective?

