01:16:48,600 --> 01:16:51,300
No sense of linear time or motion?

935
01:16:51,400 --> 01:16:52,700
Yes.

936
01:16:52,900 --> 01:16:54,600
But all-knowing, all-sensing?

937
01:16:54,800 --> 01:16:56,000
Exactly.

938
01:16:56,100 --> 01:16:58,300
- Would you care for some tea?
- Thank you.

939
01:16:58,500 --> 01:17:02,500
You know, as a scientist and atheist...

940
01:17:02,700 --> 01:17:05,500
...my mind was closed to such things.

941
01:17:05,700 --> 01:17:09,300
Oh, absolutely.
Afterlife, near-death experiences.

942
01:17:09,500 --> 01:17:12,400
Like everyone else,
I thought people saw bright lights...

943
01:17:12,600 --> 01:17:14,500
...Eden-like gardens and so forth...

944
01:17:14,700 --> 01:17:18,300
...because they were
culturally conditioned to do so.

945
01:17:18,500 --> 01:17:22,800
But after 25 years in a hospice...

946
01:17:23,000 --> 01:17:26,200
...working with people,
many of whom were pronounced dead...

947
01:17:26,900 --> 01:17:29,500
...but then miraculously survived...

948
01:17:29,700 --> 01:17:34,100
...the account of what they actually
experienced were so strikingly similar...

949
01:17:34,300 --> 01:17:36,700
...it couldn't just be coincidence.

950
01:17:38,800 --> 01:17:42,000
And add to that the fact that when
they had these experiences...

951
01:17:42,100 --> 01:17:44,400
...they were almost all unconscious...

952
01:17:44,600 --> 01:17:50,100
...a state in which my enemies agree
the brain cannot create fresh images.

953
01:17:52,400 --> 01:17:55,300
So you think I really did
experience something?

954
01:17:55,500 --> 01:17:56,800
Oh, yes.

955
01:17:58,400 --> 01:18:00,100
I think you experienced death.

956
01:18:03,800 --> 01:18:05,800
It's all here.

957
01:18:06,000 --> 01:18:10,200
I'm afraid if your journey is anything
like mine, it won't be an easy one.

958
01:18:10,400 --> 01:18:12,200
It's a lonely field to plow.

959
01:18:12,400 --> 01:18:16,600
People get quite irrational around
this subject. Quite hostile, even.

960
01:18:16,800 --> 01:18:19,900
But the evidence is irrefutable.

961
01:18:20,000 --> 01:18:21,700
I tried.

962
01:18:26,900 --> 01:18:29,200
You know, perhaps someone like you...

963
01:18:30,500 --> 01:18:34,100
...in your position, and with
your influence, can change that.

964
01:18:35,600 --> 01:18:37,100
I hope you can.

965
01:18:37,600 --> 01:18:39,200
Thank you.

966
01:18:41,300 --> 01:18:42,500
ROUSSEAU:
Good luck.

967
01:18:42,700 --> 01:18:44,300
I'll send it back when I'm done.

